Project Title
Tic Tac Toe AI using Minimax Algorithm

Introduction
This project is a simple Tic Tac Toe game built using Python.  
The player plays against an AI opponent.

Objective
The main goal of this project is to create an AI that can play Tic Tac Toe intelligently using the Minimax algorithm.

Game Description
- The game is played on a 3x3 grid  
- Player uses X  
- AI uses O  
- The goal is to get three symbols in a row  

AI Method
The AI uses the Minimax algorithm.  
It checks possible moves and chooses the best move to win or avoid losing.

Environment
- Single player game (Human vs AI)  
- Fully observable  
- Deterministic (no random moves)

Tools
- Python  
- Tkinter for GUI  
- Minimax Algorithm
